#: ../../S/semi.rst:5
msgid "semi"
msgstr "semi"

#: ../../S/semi.rst:7
msgid "/se´mee/, /se´mi:/"
msgstr "/se´mee/, /se´mi:/"

#: ../../S/semi.rst:9
msgid ""
"n\\. Abbreviation for ‘semicolon’, when speaking. \"Commands to :ref:`grind`"
" are prefixed by semi-semi-star\" means that the prefix is ``;;\\*``\\, not "
"1/4 of a star."
msgstr ""
"名詞 話すときの‘semicolon(セミコロン)’の略。「\\ :ref:`grind`\\ へのコマンドはsemi-semi-"
"starを前に付ける」とは、その接頭辞が\\ ``;;\\*``\\ であって、星の4分の1ではないという意味だ。"

#: ../../S/semi.rst:14
msgid ""
"A prefix used with words such as ‘immediately’ as a qualifier. \"When is the"
" system coming up?\" \"Semi-immediately.\" (That is, maybe not for an hour.)"
" \"We did consider that possibility semi-seriously.\" See also "
":ref:`infinite`\\."
msgstr ""
"‘immediately(直ちに)’のような語と一緒に修飾語として使われる接頭辞。「システムはいつ立ち上がるの?」「Semi-"
"immediately(半ば直ちに)。」(つまり、ひょっとすると1時間は来ないかもしれない。)「我々はその可能性をsemi-"
"seriously(半ば真剣に)検討した。」\\ :ref:`infinite`\\ も参照。"
